@deffn {Function} lambert_w (@var{z})
The principal branch of Lambert's W function W(z) (@urldlmf{4.13}), the solution of 
m4_displaymath(
<<<z = W(z)e^{W(z)}>>>,
@math{z = W(z) * exp(W(z))})  
